<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
    body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .navbar {
        background-color: #0a3d62;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .navbar-nav .nav-link {
        color: #fff;
    }

    .hero {
        margin-top:100px;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 50px 0px;
        text-align: left;
        margin-left:-30px;
       
    }

        .hero h1 {
            color: #0a3d62;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .hero p {
            color:black;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

    .search-form {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

        .search-form .form-control {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #1e90ff;
        border: none;
    }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #1c86ee;
        }

    
    .gif-container {
        margin-top:-60px;
        
        text-align: center; 
    }

    .gif-container img {
        max-width: 130%; 
        height: auto; 
        display: block; 
        margin: 0 30px; 
        
    }

    </style>

</head>
<body>


    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h1>Find a place where you can be yourself</h1>
                    <p>If you are looking for a place where you can be yourself, don't give up. Keep searching until you find a place that feels like home.</p>
                    <div class="search-form">
                        <form class="form-inline">
                            <div class="form-group mr-2">
                                <label for="wantTo" class="sr-only">Want to</label>
                                <select class="form-control" id="wantTo">
                                    <option>Buy</option>
                                    <option>Rent</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group mr-2">
                                <label for="propertyType" class="sr-only">Property Type</label>
                                <select class="form-control" id="propertyType">
                                    <option>Apartment</option>
                                    <option>House</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group mr-2">
                                <label for="location" class="sr-only">Location</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="location" placeholder="Street, City, Zip ...">
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Search</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 gif-container">
                    <img src="~/Content/house.png" alt="Animation">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
